lastfm.summary: "Lone Digger" is a song by the French electro swing group Caravan Palace from their third studio album <|°_°|> (also known as Robot Face or Robot) released on 16 October, 2015. The song was released as a single on 18 September, 2015. As of December 2019, the song "Lone Digger" was certified gold by RIAA. And as of June 2023, the song's animated music video has gained over 380 million views on YouTube. The song was also featured in the 2022 Disney movie Strange World. Read more on Last.fm.
lastfm.title: Lone Digger
